# Heel-Kawn Multiplayer Mod – Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

---

## [0.1.0] – Tech Level I Foundation (2025-09-12)
- Initial BepInEx plugin (`HeelKawnMinimal.cs`) with logging and stub TwitchBot.
- TwitchBot parses basic chat commands (`!join`, `!move`, `!pray`) (stub only, no real IRC).
- `PlayerManager`: player registry, unique codes, action queue, join/move commands.
- `VillageManager`: basic village and kingdom tracking, assignment stubs.
- `WorldBoxAPIHelper`: stubs for spawning/moving villagers (logs only).
- `ActionQueueProcessor`: action tick loop for queued moves (no in-game integration yet).
- `ConfigManager`: loads Twitch credentials and config.
- Project structure and roadmap docs (`README.md`, `TechTreeRoadmap.md`).
- Contribution guide (`CONTRIBUTING.md`).

---

## [Unreleased]
- Tech Level II: Real Twitch IRC multiplayer.
- Action-driven villager spawning/movement in WorldBox.
- Player persistence and more extensive kingdom logic.
- Expanded commands: farming, building, trait/prayer system.
- See [`TechTreeRoadmap.md`](TechTreeRoadmap.md) for next planned features.
